        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our worthless house of straw we build in vain no more;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We gather wood in one accord His dwelling to restore;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Clean homes, fling wide the doors; greet sinners from all shores;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Bring in the sheaves with shouts of joy, the flock lead to the Lord."
            }
          ]
        }
